name: Optimus Prime
detail_description: Lead the Autobots into battle with this impressive Optimus Prime action figure. It can transform between robot and truck modes and comes with a blaster accessory.

name: Megatron
detail_description: Unleash the power of the Decepticons with this formidable Megatron action figure. It features intricate detailing, a fusion cannon accessory, and multiple points of articulation.

name: Bumblebee
detail_description: Get ready for action-packed adventures with this Bumblebee action figure. It can transform into a sleek sports car and comes with a blaster weapon.

name: Darth Vader
detail_description: Embrace the power of the dark side with this Darth Vader action figure. It features a removable helmet, lightsaber accessory, and a display stand.

name: Rey
detail_description: Join the fight against the First Order with this Rey action figure. It comes with a staff, blaster, and multiple points of articulation for dynamic poses.

name: Yoda
detail_description: Train in the ways of the Force with this Yoda action figure. It features realistic facial details, a lightsaber, and a cane accessory.

name: Iron Man
detail_description: Bring the armored Avenger to life with this highly detailed Iron Man action figure. It features multiple points of articulation and comes with interchangeable accessories.

name: Spider-Man
detail_description: Swing into action with this amazing Spider-Man action figure. It features a web-slinging pose, interchangeable hands, and a display base inspired by the city skyline.

name: Black Widow
detail_description: Unleash the deadly skills of Black Widow with this action figure. It comes with various weapons, a dynamic stand, and highly detailed features to capture the essence of the super-spy.
